Alma Rock Phillips https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alma_Rock_Phillips 0 Alma Rock Phillips was an Australian actor of stage and screen. She appeared in a number of early Australian silent films. She was the daughter of Rock Phillips. Alma_Rock_Phillips was an_Australian_actor of stage_and_screen . She appeared in a_number of early_Australian_silent_films .
